HUBCO Inc to acquire Hometown Bancorp Inc . Hometown Bancorp Inc said Wednesday its shareholders had agreed to let HUBCO acquire it . Hometown , parent company of The Bank of Darien , said the shareholders approved the acquisition by the Mahwah , N . J . , bank at a special meeting on August 20 . The acquisition , subject to approval by the Connecticut banking department , would likely occur at the end of August , it added . Hometown said each outstanding common share would be converted into the right to receive $ 17 . 75 in cash . - - New York Newsdesk 212 859 - 1610 
